    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Cylindrical, or spool-shaped rings with pierced or openwork sides, or stands used to support hot dishes and protect the surface below.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
